{
  "id": "nce2-l27",
  "title": "Lesson 27: A Wet Night",
  "audio": "/audio/nce2/27ÔºçA Wet Night.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.png",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What happened to the boys in the night?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.29,
      "endTime": 15.07
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Late in the afternoon, the boys put up their tent in the middle of a field.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 15.08,
      "endTime": 21.84
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "As soon as this was done, they cooked a meal over an open fire.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 21.85,
      "endTime": 27.97
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "They were all hungry and the food smelled good.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 27.98,
      "endTime": 32.98
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "After a wonderful meal, they told stories and sang songs by the campfire.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 32.99,
      "endTime": 40.9
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But some time later it began to rain.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 40.91,
      "endTime": 44.7
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The boys felt tired so they put out the fire and crept into their tent.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 44.71,
      "endTime": 51.46
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Their sleeping bags were warm and comfortable, so they all slept soundly.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 51.47,
      "endTime": 58.65
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In the middle of the night, two boys woke up and began shouting.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 58.66,
      "endTime": 64.54
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The tent was full of water!",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 64.55,
      "endTime": 67.55
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "They all leapt out of their sleeping bags and hurried outside.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 67.56,
      "endTime": 73.64
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It was raining heavily and they found that a stream had formed in the field.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 73.65,
      "endTime": 80.08
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The stream wound its way across the field and then flowed right under their tent!",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 80.09,
      "endTime": 85.09
    }
  ]
}